                    ('A "quote dump" in an essay is problematic because:', ['It presents evidence without explaining how it supports the argument, leaving the analytical work undone', 'It uses too many short quotations instead of long ones', 'Quotations from primary sources are not allowed in AP® essays', 'It makes the essay too long to read effectively']),
