                    ('Bias in a source:', ['Does not automatically disqualify it, but requires considering whether the perspective distorts or suppresses important information', 'Always disqualifies the source from use in an AP® essay', 'Is only present in sources written by individuals, not institutions', 'Is easy to detect from the source\'s title alone']),
