                ['https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNw8ij8rejM', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNw8ij8rejM'],
                ['Whose argument should dominate a synthesis essay: yours or the sources\'?', 'What happens when sources dominate and the writer\'s voice disappears?', 'How do you handle sources that contradict your thesis?']
